#: content/_index.md:57
msgid "What’s in it for you"
msgstr ""

#: content/_index.md:58
msgid ""
"Remember when Linux was an undiscovered country and everything was new and "
"fun? KDE Linux is that all over again: we’re creating the operating system "
"of the future with the clout and resources of KDE behind it, and you can be "
"part of it. Here, individual efforts make a difference on a global scale."
msgstr ""

#: content/_index.md:60
msgid ""
"{{< linux/button src=\"/docs/kde-linux-dev\" description=\"Contribute to KDE"
" Linux\" >}} {{< /section >}}"
msgstr ""

